  "comment": {
    "text": "This is the body text of a dialog box that appears when a user chooses to disconnect their Telegram account. It informs the user that their account is currently connected for notifications and explains the consequence of disconnecting. The `{{username}}` variable will be replaced with the user's Telegram username.",
